## Common Colab Issues
**Problem**: Can't install packages
**Solution**: Try restarting runtime, use `!pip install --user package_name`

**Problem**: GPU not available  
**Solution**: Check Runtime > Change runtime type > Hardware accelerator > GPU

**Problem**: Session disconnects frequently
**Solution**: Keep tab active, consider Colab Pro for longer sessions

## Hugging Face Issues
**Problem**: Model loading errors
**Solution**: Check model name spelling, try different model sizes

**Problem**: Out of memory errors
**Solution**: Use smaller models, reduce batch size, clear cache

## General Python Issues
**Problem**: Import errors
**Solution**: Install missing packages, check spelling, restart kernel

**Problem**: Slow performance
**Solution**: Use GPU when available, optimize batch sizes

## Getting Help
1. Check this troubleshooting guide
2. Search GitHub Issues
3. Ask in Discussions
4. Join community forums
